channel.title: Delta++
channel.description: Hey guys, I've always wanted to try a Delta source, but never had the time to do so. So now I do have the time, and I decided to download Delta ++, from what I've heard it seems to be a good source, but the download links are down. So if anyone had this source/its client, then please post a link here. Any other alternatives are also good!
